Name: Aster
Notes: Primary cosmic goddess, catgirl creatrix of the universe, Alpha figure who spun the cosmos from yarn and filled it with milk

Name: Andromeda
Notes: Companion goddess created by Aster, catgirl with dark skin and flowing hair, Omega figure representing the end of all, counterpart to Aster

Name: Triangulum
Notes: Cosmic entity, galaxy formed from broken yarn threads between Aster and Andromeda

Name: Magellan
Notes: Cosmic entity, clouds formed from broken yarn threads between Aster and Andromeda

Name: Sagittarius
Notes: Constellation/cosmic region, referenced as part of the cosmic love story

Name: Princess
Notes: Celestial entity, likely referring to Andromeda constellation, part of the cosmic reunion hope

Name: Milkdromeda
Notes: Future cosmic entity, the unified form that Aster and Andromeda will become when reunited
